## 12. NEVER

- Never invent, guess, or hard-code a clinical value
- Never render clinical content without source + review
- Never make the app direct treatment for a specific patient
- Never send identifiable health data off-region / to offshore models
- Never commit secrets; never skip plan on non-trivial work
- Never reproduce licensed reference content (SAMF/MIMS/Lexicomp)
- Never ship with an open S0
